# TradeFlow
Institutional-grade trading intelligence terminal engineered for high-performance traders. TradeFlow combines real-time analytics, AI-powered behavioral coaching, advanced journaling, and portfolio intelligence into a unified trading workspace.

**Tech Stack:** Next.js 15, TypeScript, FastAPI, MongoDB, TailwindCSS

### Key Features
- Multi-environment trading workspace for intraday and swing traders
- Real-time watchlists with browser alerts and sector categorization
- AI trading coach for execution grading, edge discovery, and overtrading prevention
- Interactive analytics including P&L heatmaps and sector exposure tracking
- Secure JWT authentication with isolated per-user data architecture

Link: thetradeflow.vercel.app

